reviewText: It doesn't tell you anything about how to deal with Restless Leg Syndrome. It just lets you know a lot of people have it and what it feels like. I already know that! I was hoping to get some tips on how to subdue it or make it stop when I cannot take my medicine (which is limited to one pill a day and only lasts for 8-12 hours). Totally wasted my money on this video.
